{1010}{}{Too much stuff}
{1020}{}{ }
{2000}{}{Well hello.  What  do you need?}
{2010}{}{I would like to receive a fake small gun.}
{2020}{}{Give me a certain big gun...}
{2030}{}{What's in your stock of energy weaponry?}
{2040}{}{Something to bash my opponents with!}
{2050}{}{Something to throw, perhaps?}
{2060}{}{A body armor.}
{2070}{}{Show me the upgrade blueprints.}
{2080}{}{Nothing.}
{3000}{}{Here you go.}
{4000}{}{Slow down a bit, you've taken enough for now.}
{5000}{}{What gun would that be?}
{5010}{}{A 14mm Pistol.}
