{8040}{}{A Super Sledgehammer.}
{8050}{}{A Wakizashi Blade.}
{8060}{}{Your ex wife...}
{8070}{}{I want something to zbitten a synnek! Blyat!}
{9000}{}{And what exactly?}
{9010}{}{Eight frags, please.}
{9020}{}{I'll take eight plasma ones.}
{9030}{}{Actually... You have some Spears in stock?}
{9040}{}{Give me some Throwing Knifes, please.}
{10000}{}{What kind of armor?}
{10010}{}{A Leather Armor mark II.}
{10020}{}{A Combat Leather Jacket.}
