{10040}{}{A Tesla Armor.}
{10050}{}{A Combat Armor.}
{10060}{}{One suit of Combat Armor mark II.}
{10070}{}{One suit of Desert Combat Armor.}
{10080}{}{A bath ro(p)e please.}
{11000}{}{Sorry, no. Even if those are fake weapons, I don't believe they can be safely given to someone with your... condition. You can still watch the fights, while you are here.}
{11010}{}{Uh?}
